@QAAutomation.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5018

### List all active evaluation forms
GET {{QAAutomation.API_HostAddress}}/api/evaluationforms
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single evaluation form by id
GET {{QAAutomation.API_HostAddress}}/api/evaluationforms/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new custom evaluation form
POST {{QAAutomation.API_HostAddress}}/api/evaluationforms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Code Review Checklist",
  "description": "Standard code review evaluation form",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Code Quality",
      "order": 1,
      "fields": [
        { "label": "Readability", "fieldType": 2, "isRequired": true, "order": 1, "maxRating": 5 },
        { "label": "Test Coverage", "fieldType": 2, "isRequired": true, "order": 2, "maxRating": 5 },
        { "label": "Comments", "fieldType": 1, "isRequired": false, "order": 3 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

###

### Submit an evaluation result
POST {{QAAutomation.API_HostAddress}}/api/evaluationresults
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formId": 1,
  "evaluatedBy": "reviewer@example.com",
  "notes": "Overall good quality",
  "scores": [
    { "fieldId": 1, "value": "4", "numericValue": 4 },
    { "fieldId": 2, "value": "5", "numericValue": 5 }
  ]
}

###

### Get all evaluation results for a form
GET {{QAAutomation.API_HostAddress}}/api/evaluationresults/byform/1
Accept: application/json

###
